"Storyteller Export Summary

Project: Interview Layers
Target: Final Cut Pro — Rough Cut Export (Beta)
Timeline: 0:33
Generated: 2026-06-25T12:00:00.000Z

Exported:
  ✓ 3 A-roll clips
  ✓ 0 markers
  ✓ 1 source file

Not included in interchange timeline:
  • 1 B-roll clip
  • 1 title overlay
  • 1 sound effect placement

Includes primary edit (A-roll rough cut), media, and timeline metadata. B-roll, graphics, and advanced layering are provided in manifest.json for manual finishing while Final Cut XML compatibility continues to improve.

Editorial contract:
  • Clip order preserved
  • Trim in/out preserved
  • Timeline duration preserved (within one frame)
  • Source media packaged when available locally

Manifest clips: 0 total references · schema v1
See manifest.json for complete timeline metadata."
`;

